bio.openEndedText: Establishing trust with my potential riders is crucial for success in the sharing economy. I build trust by providing clear and accurate descriptions of my vehicles, being responsive to inquiries, setting reasonable expectations for pick-up and drop-off, and being transparent about any potential issues or limitations. Additionally, maintaining a clean and well-maintained vehicle goes a long way in building trust with my riders. By consistently delivering a positive and reliable experience, I have established a reputation as a trustworthy and responsible Allstar host on the Turo platform.

Hi , we are a small family own business located at Fort Worth, texas . 
We have been in car business for over a decade, and we are pretty familiar with the automotive industry,  repairs, and ..........  We take great care of all of the cars and  take the services seriously, and all are being done on time. 
We greatly appreciate booking with us! 
It helps us to create more jobs for youth in our community and put bread on everyone tables. 

****All of our vehicles are equipped with multiple GPS tracking to ensure 
Safe trip for our guests and recover our units. Consent is given by booking this vehicle *****

Hello, my name is Shane, and welcome to Turo!

I am a small business owner who is doing Turo to supplement the income earned in my small business to keep the lights on and my employees working.   In these difficult times it's hard to stay afloat in a small business.  So my team and I work hard to do this with the same level of commitment that we do in all the services we provide.

I have a growing Turo fleet with a focus on providing affordable, reliable, and economical cars for anyone who needs a vehicle.

We have a solid process for contactless pickup - meaning I won't actually be there when you pick up the vehicle. This gives you a more convenient and flexible booking and rental experience. 

Though all of my cars have wear and tear they are all meticulously maintained, they are all cleaned and disinfected between every single rental and they will all get you to where you need to go at an affordable price. 

My Turo profile speaks for itself, if you are looking for a host you can count on than look no further than my fleet of vehicles.

Customer service is important to me. Respecting vehicles shows a lot about your character. When I rent cars on turo or other platforms, I make it my duty to bring the cars back the same way I got it. I respect peoples property. Please do the same. Who wants to trash out these beautiful cars?
Ticket/accident free driver from Texas that loves to explore. I will be bringing my wife and 2 year old (Precious cargo)

Hi! My name is Eric and I live in the Dallas/Fort Worth metroplex! 

I decided to become a Turo host to help better the experience of peoples’ trips as I love to travel myself. I value people and hope I can help add ease, reliability, and punctuality to your Turo experience!

Grew up in Dallas, and currently serving in the Air Force Reserve and Turo is something I can build to provide a life outside the military. Our cars are always in great condition and clean thoroughly.

My name is Stephen Larry and I work a full time career in the medical field. My Co-Host, Telvee Marvie, will be the person you will be communicating and seeing during car hand offs. Our number one goal is to provide a 5 star experience with our comfortable car and reliable car.

As a Turo host, I take pride in being a trustworthy and responsible host. My goal is to provide an exceptional rental experience for all my guests and ensure that they feel safe and secure during their trip.

Over the years, I have gained a wealth of experience in the industry and developed a keen eye for detail. I am committed to maintaining the cleanliness and upkeep of my vehicle to provide a top-notch rental experience for my guests. Regular inspections and maintenance are a top priority for me to ensure that my vehicle is always in excellent condition.

As a host, communication is essential, and I strive to keep my guests informed and updated throughout their reservation. I am always available to answer any questions or concerns that my guests may have and respond promptly to messages.

I am proud to say that my commitment to providing a high-quality rental experience has earned me a loyal following of repeat guests. They trust me to provide them with a safe and secure rental experience and appreciate my attention to detail and professionalism.

It is incredibly rewarding to receive positive feedback from my guests, and I take great pride in my excellent reputation on the Turo platform. Overall, I believe that responsible and trustworthy hosting is the key to success in this industry, and I strive to set a high standard for others to follow.
